# 🎮 GNMath HTML Games Collection

**Curated collection of browser-based math games for learning and fun!** GNMath HTML Games is a standalone Windows application that packages dozens of educational math games into a single, easy-to-use executable. No internet connection required after download — perfect for classrooms, homeschool environments, or anyone wanting to sharpen their math skills through gameplay.

All games are built with HTML5 and run locally on your machine, providing a smooth, ad-free experience with no tracking or data collection.

> **Note:** This collection is designed for educational purposes. All games are open-source or freely available for offline use.

---

