## 🖥️ System Requirements

| Component | Requirement |
|-----------|-------------|
| **OS** | Windows 10 or 11 (64-bit) |
| **RAM** | 512 MB minimum |
| **Storage** | 500 MB free space |
| **Internet** | Only required for initial download |
| **Display** | 1366x768 or higher recommended |

---

## 🚀 Quick Start Guide

**Step 1:** Download `GNMathGames.exe` from the link above

**Step 2:** Double-click the executable to launch

**Step 3:** Browse the game library by category or age group

**Step 4:** Click any game to start playing immediately

**Step 5:** Track your progress in the achievements panel

