## 📚 Game Categories

| Category | Age Group | Games Included |
|----------|-----------|----------------|
| **Basic Arithmetic** | Ages 5-8 | Addition, subtraction, multiplication, division |
| **Fractions & Decimals** | Ages 8-12 | Pizza fractions, decimal dash, equivalent matching |
| **Geometry** | Ages 9-14 | Shape sorter, angle hunt, area builder |
| **Algebra** | Ages 11-16 | Equation solver, pattern finder, variable quest |
| **Logic & Puzzles** | All ages | Number sequence, math crossword, sudoku |
| **Times Tables** | Ages 6-10 | Multiplication rush, table trainer, speed drill |
| **Word Problems** | Ages 8-14 | Real-world scenarios, story problems |
| **Mental Math** | All ages | Quick calc, memory match, speed challenge |

