## 🎮 Featured Games

| Game | Description | Skills |
|------|-------------|--------|
| **Math Rush** | Race against time to solve equations | Mental math, speed |
| **Fraction Pizzeria** | Serve customers by slicing pizzas correctly | Fractions, division |
| **Geometry Builder** | Create shapes using perimeter and area formulas | Geometry, measurement |
| **Algebra Adventure** | Solve equations to progress through levels | Algebra, problem-solving |
| **Number Ninja** | Slice through correct answers | Basic operations |
| **Coin Counter** | Count money and make change | Decimals, real-world math |
| **Pattern Detective** | Find the missing number in sequences | Logic, patterns |
| **Math Bingo** | Classic bingo with math problems | All operations |

