---

## 🔧 Troubleshooting

| Issue | Solution |
|-------|----------|
| **Game won't launch** | Run as Administrator, check antivirus exceptions |
| **No sound** | Check Windows volume mixer, enable in settings |
| **Slow performance** | Close other applications, update graphics drivers |
| **Games not loading** | Reinstall application, check file integrity |
| **Progress not saving** | Check write permissions in install folder |
| **Display issues** | Update display drivers, adjust resolution |

