## ❓ Frequently Asked Questions

**Q: Is this completely free?**  
A: Yes, all games are free with no in-app purchases or subscriptions.

**Q: Does it work without internet?**  
A: Absolutely! Once downloaded, all games run completely offline.

**Q: Can teachers use this in classrooms?**  
A: Yes, the app includes teacher tools, progress tracking, and curriculum alignment.

**Q: Are there ads?**  
A: No ads whatsoever — just pure educational gameplay.

**Q: Can I track multiple students?**  
A: Yes, create individual profiles for each student with separate progress tracking.

**Q: What age groups is this for?**  
A: Games range from kindergarten through high school level.

**Q: Does it work on tablets?**  
A: This Windows version is for PCs only. Tablet versions available separately.

